                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="content__page-desc">
                <h3>Countertop dishwashers</h3>
                <p>
                  Are compact and sit on the counter, making them suitable for small kitchens or apartments. They connect to the kitchen faucet and are easy to set up and use. Common repair issues include water inlet problems and drainage blockages. Ensuring a secure connection to the faucet and checking for leaks can prevent most issues. Regular maintenance includes cleaning the interior and checking the spray arms to ensure they are not clogged.
                </p>
