                        7-10 years. If your microwave is nearing or has exceeded
                        this age, replacement might be the better option.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <b>Technology and Features: </b>Newer models may offer
                        improved efficiency, better safety features, and
                        advanced cooking options that an older model lacks.
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    <h3>Overall Condition</h3>
                    <ul>
